text.section:
An emergency permit:
Shall be valid for a period of time not to exceed thirty (30) days;
Shall not be renewed or reissued and shall be immediately canceled if a medical emergency no longer exists;
May be canceled by the executive director upon reasonable cause without a prior hearing; and
Shall not authorize a physician assistant to practice beyond a specified geographical area, beyond the scope of practice encompassed by the medical emergency, or without the supervision of a supervising physician.
